indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - DTH
indicators.description: Number of malaria deaths reported by health facilities (public, private and NGO) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Deaths
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports recieved Deaths

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - IPD
indicators.description: Number of inpatient malaria cases reported by health facilities (public, private and NGO) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Inpatient
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports recieved Inpatient

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - OPD
indicators.description: Number of outpatient malaria cases reported by health facilities (public, private, NGO and community) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Outpatient
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports received Outpatient

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Confirmed malaria cases
indicators.description: Cases confirmed as positive with microscopy and/or RDT

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Foci identified (new+old) in past 5 years (including current calendar year)
indicators.shortName: Foci identified, new and old (list of foci)
indicators.description: Number of malaria foci identified (new+old) identified in the past 5 years (including current calendar year)
indicators.numeratorDescription: Foci identified (new+old) in past 5 years (including current calendar year)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Malaria cases classified as local
indicators.description: Number of cases confirmed as malaria that are investigated and classified as either indiginous or introduced

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Percentage of P. falciparum
indicators.description: Percentage of positive cases due to P. falciparum (Number of cases due to P. falciparum divided by all positives multiplied by 100)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Percentage of P. vivax
indicators.description: Percentage of positive cases due to P. vivax (Number of cases due to P. falciparum divided by all positives multiplied by 100)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of foci classified
indicators.description: Number of foci investigated and classified divided by total number of foci in the registry multipled by 100 (in ayear)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of foci investigated
indicators.description: Number of foci investigated divided by total number of foci in the registry multipled by 100 (in ayear)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of foci with zero local cases
indicators.shortName: Proportion of foci with zero local cases
indicators.description: Number of foci with zero local cases and divided by total number of foci in the registry multipled by 100 (in ayear)
indicators.numeratorDescription: Foci classified as endemic or active (with confirmed local cases for at least the past 2 years)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of malaria cases classified
indicators.description: Number of positive cases investigated and classified divided ny total number of cases investigated multiplied by 00

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of malaria cases investigated
indicators.description: Number of positive cases detected through PCD and investigated by total number of cases detected through PCD multiplied by 00
